java.util.prefs
Class NodeChangeEvent

java.lang.Object
  java.util.EventObject
      java.util.prefs.NodeChangeEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class NodeChangeEvent
extends EventObject
implements Serializable

This is the event class to indicate that one child of the preference node has been added or deleted.

Please note that the serialization functionality has not yet been implemented, so the serialization methods do nothing but throw a NotSerializableException.

Since:
Android 1.0
See Also:
